snippet.title: Star Wars First Assault (Gameplay Trailer)
snippet.description: Gameplay and trailer leaked on the internet for a short time for the new Star wars 1st person shooter for xbox live arcade. Apparently if this game sells good a Battlefront 3 will be made.
